Direct Known Subclasses:
BinaryRelation, NaryRelation
public abstract class Relation extends Classifier<Relation,RelationStereotype>
A classifier that defines the properties of a set of relations of the subject domain. Examples include "studies in", "buys product from" (ternary relation), and derivation relations (e.g., between material relations and relators).
